items.description:
Tilla is your new app to keep track of all your subscriptions without any limitations. Manage your subscriptions and get notified when a bill is due.

Easily add your subscription
Tracking your subscriptions has never been easier, just choose any from the bundled subscriptions or add your own, fill in the simple details and you are ready to go, Tilla will do the rest for you!

Your subscriptions are in your hands
Tilla provides a clear overview of all your subscriptions and upcoming payments. You will always know the amount of money spent every month on the subscriptions and never miss a payment date.

Get notified
Tilla also notifies you when a bill date is due, so you will never have to deal with late payment fees you didn't know about. Reminders are also are highly customizable for your comfort.

Even more features with "Premium"
• Unlimited count of subscriptions;
• Track and optimize your spendings with "Analytics";
• Cloud synchronization between devices;
• Local backups on a device;
• And more features coming in the future!
